description:
Expand your track list with the Party Classics Vol. 2 Song Pack! You need the full game Let's Sing Country to use this DLC. Includes hit songs:
• A-Ha "Take On Me"
• Tears for Fears "Mad World"
• Blondie "Heart of Glass"
• New Order "Blue Monday"
• Queen "We will Rock You"
name: Let's Sing - Party Classics Vol. 2 Song Pack
